IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. CALLDEMO.
PROCEDURE DIVISION.
    CALL "SUBPROG".
    CALL WS-PROG-NAME.
    CALL "PAYROLL" USING WS-EMP-ID WS-HOURS.
    CALL "COMPUTE-TAX" USING BY REFERENCE WS-GROSS
        BY CONTENT WS-RATE BY VALUE 100 RETURNING WS-NET END-CALL.
    CALL WS-HANDLER USING BY CONTENT "literal-arg" WS-FLAG
        RETURNING WS-STATUS.
    STOP RUN.
